Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.88,0:23:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Smile on his face, tears running down her cheeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,koko ni suteteyukenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to go ahead, they should not be forgotten.
